 *     @type string       $test_file_sizefter            HTML or text to append to each link. Default is `</p>`.
 *     @type string       $section_titles_before      HTML or text to prepend to each link, inside the `<a>` tag.
 *                                          Also prepended to the current item, which is not linked. Default empty.
 *     @type string       $section_titles_after       HTML or text to append to each Pages link inside the `<a>` tag.
